            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Test prompt: "Minimal portfolio for UX designer, dark mode, smooth animations." Framer AI generated site in 47 seconds. Showed to 5 professional designers. 4 said "I'd hire this designer." One said "Better than my current portfolio." AI design quality is shockingly good now.</p>
