          <span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Framer sites convert 23% better than competitors</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">A/B test: same service business, different builders. Framer site converted 23% of visitors to leads. Squarespace: 14%. Wix: 11%. Design quality = trust = conversions. Framer's aesthetic advantage directly impacts revenue.</p>
